        <h2>Basketball-Specific Planning</h2>
        <p>Basketball teams are typically 12-20 players, making banquets more intimate than football. This allows for more personalized touches and larger individual awards.</p>

        <h3>Basketball Decor Themes</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Hoops Central</strong> — Basketball court-themed tables with painted lines, mini hoops as centerpiece elements</li>
          <li><strong>Bracket Busters</strong> — Highlight the season's tournament journey with bracket displays</li>
          <li><strong>Hardwood Classic</strong> — More formal, wood-accented decorations with team colors</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="product-note">
          <p><strong>🏀 Basketball Centerpieces:</strong> Custom 3D printed basketball centerpieces available in 7" and 9" sizes. The 9" option includes full personalization — team name, player name, and jersey number. Perfect for banquet tables and senior keepsakes.</p>
          <a href="https://lakeshore-gift.myshopify.com/products/basketball-banquet-table-centerpiece-7-ball" class="btn btn-outline" target="_blank">View Basketball Centerpieces →</a>
        </div>

        <h2>Basketball Award Ideas</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Team MVP</strong></li>
          <li><strong>Most Improved Player</strong></li>
          <li><strong>Defensive Stopper Award</strong></li>
          <li><strong>Sixth Man/Woman of the Year</strong></li>
          <li><strong>Free Throw Champion</strong> — Highest FT percentage</li>
          <li><strong>Three Point Leader</strong></li>
          <li><strong>Assist Leader</strong></li>
          <li><strong>Hustle Award</strong> — The player who made the extra effort plays</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Basketball Program Traditions</h2>
        <p>Many basketball programs have unique senior night traditions. Some do a full team warmup then recognize seniors mid-court at center court. Others present framed jerseys or personalized basketballs. Consider having seniors sit at a special head table at the banquet with their own custom basketball centerpiece as a table marker.</p>

        <p><a href="/banquet-planning/" class="btn btn-outline">Full Banquet Guide →</a> <a href="/senior-night/" class="btn btn-outline">Senior Night Guide →</a></p>
      </div>
